OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Retail sales fell in August as the rise
OL,6, in the cost of living put pressure on  
OL,7, households, official figures show.     
OL,9,FSales fell by 1.6%, continuing a slide 
OL,10,Fsince summer last year after           
OL,11,Fhospitality restrictions were lifted,  
OL,12,Fthe Office for National Statistics     
OL,13,F(ONS) said.                            
OL,15,FRetail sales in all the main sectors - 
OL,16,Ffood, non-food, online and fuel - fell 
OL,17,Fover the month, the ONS said.          
OL,19,FSupermarkets' sales volumes also fell  
OL,20,Fby 0.9% in August.                     
